name: Barney Error (15 Chances)
description:
Here is a Barney Error that has 15 chances. Press F11 to go fullscreen. Press space to turn off the computer.

When you need to enter the code, type 4 8 15 16 23 42 

Entering that code will make you win.

If you wait an hour while Barney is still happy, you will win as well. (You likely wont do this though)
